column8: Mostly clear. Winds northerly 15 to 25 km/h.

Cloudy. The chance of fog in the early morning. Medium (60%) chance of drizzle, most likely in the morning. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting south to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h early in the morning.
Partly cloudy. Areas of early fog. Winds west to northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light early in the morning then northwest to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the early afternoon.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Winds northerly 15 to 25 km/h increasing to 25 to 40 km/h during the morning then shifting south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the afternoon.
Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 15 to 20 km/h turning east to southeasterly during the morning.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting south to southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 15 to 25 km/h.
Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 15 to 25 km/h.
